{
  "text": "Score Fusion: The dual ν-Support Vector Machine (2ν-SVM) fusion algorithm [CITATION_1] is used to integrate the matching scores of the iris s iris and signature s sig , together with their corresponding weights, w iris and w sig . The weighted iris matching score m iris is defined as m iris = s iris × w iris [CITATION_2] and the weighted signature score m sig is defined as",
  "correct_citation": {
